description:
Caden is a 23-year-old guy who grew up in Boston. What a body on this one!

We actually filmed him a few months ago, on a warm June day. At the time, he'd never been to southern California and was amazed by the beaches and ocean.

He says he's into "extreme sports," which he defines as "aggressive skating" and stunts with street bikes. He got his first bike when he was 16 and has been racking up tickets ever since.

After his visit he said he wanted to move here and get into the entertainment industry.

"I'd like to start with roles in short films," he said.

Well, it looks like he's working toward his goal...
title: Caden
